attachments.displayName:
Love runs deeper than you knew yesterday
pray m(eye)n goes deep enough
to stand strong enough

Waves crashing upon our beach
stealing out from under US our Pride
eye can not let us be beat

<you listen and heard why i am willing to fight>
< it's not you not the day nor the table of Knight >

Joy jumps in my heart and Soul
Loving gentle kindness made whole
some say we are the Heart of Gold
Look i jump now i jump now i jump now
Joyful days cometh it is best i spook that Truth

Listen in the calmness brought to US words scary truth
falsehoods burning embers spreads
like poison running into shallow water  .. deemed
"not be safe to drink"

We are designated Lifeguards at this local beach
Go and be enjoying the fruits of hard Labor
Go administer medicine of Mind Body Spirit
Honoring blessed brotherhood

MEN neighbors <and Geeks>

































anoblefellow . ANF 2013
